text: The 1952 Navy Midshipmen football team represented the United States Naval Academy (USNA) during the 1952 college football season. Navy competed as an independent with no conference affiliation. The team was led by third-year head coach Eddie Erdelatz. ==Schedule== ==Personnel== ==References== Navy Midshipmen Category:Navy Midshipmen football seasons Category:1952 in sports in Maryland
